(18, 1, '2018-05-25 09:15:55', '2018-05-25 09:15:55', 'It gives me immense pride and satisfaction to share with you the phenomenal growth that NAZ Group as an organization has witnessed. Our success is attributed to our ability to stay ahead of competition by consistently investing in our staff to develop their skills with latest technology and operations.', 'Nazz Success', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nazz-success', '', '', '2018-05-25 09:15:55', '2018-05-25 09:15:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=18', 0, 'post', '', 0),
