(35, 1, '2018-05-25 09:26:11', '2018-05-25 09:26:11', 'We at Nazz Express company provide end-to-end Shipping &amp; Logistics solutions to the Middle East region, covering wide scope of logistical needs and wants. We developed customized transport techniques, and multimodal transport operations for AIR, ROAD, and MARINE.\r\n\r\nWe take pride in our knowledge in the region like no one else being the leaders in our domain for almost than two decades. We provide simplicity and ease of operation but with professional touch to boost your business. E-commerce has established itself in the Arab World with extraordinary growth rates that exceeded all expectations; it has thus become the center of our attention and resources.', 'Who We Are', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'who-we-are', '', '', '2018-05-25 09:34:17', '2018-05-25 09:34:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=35', 0, 'post', '', 0),
